description:
If you want to know who controls you, look at who you’re not allowed to criticize. If the government is truly correct in this “pandemic” situation ... Well shouldn’t they be able to have a argument for every specialist who points out a different view? A view that could impact the lives of billions of people? Would it be really necessary to just silence them all? Does that seem logic to you? 🙄You know when you want your child to do something and they ask why?? And you’re respond is because I said so?? Doesn’t 2020 feel like that?? We’re all doing what we’re told because daddy-state said so?? We decide for them ... because they need our guidance ... but do all the adults in the world need that now too?? Have we all turned into small children who can’t decide for themselves?? #askingforafriend
